          // Define a range of dates you want to generate
          val startDate = LocalDate.of(2020, 1, 1)
          /*
          * The most recent supported end date has to be at least 15 months in the past from now. Otherwise the restriction to not create
          * any future readings will block specific test cases from succeeding.
          * */
